{"tid":741023,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（睇書巴絲入）有冇咩書會令到你地感觸反思","createTime":"2018-07-13T10:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T14:40:50.000Z","uid":6005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5169359445c41220cd3a1b3df5bd2f9805583aa3","tid":741023,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"以前細個嗰時睇小王子都只係覺得好無聊，完全睇唔明。但人大左再睇翻，真係會令到自己感觸落淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以想問吓各位巴絲有冇小王子呢type嘅書推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cfd8f891f70bb584c098c112fb7350608f74e8","tid":741023,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:35:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"704837262dd41e03e5b816bf000dc51a79254d20","tid":741023,"uid":90282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"Mitch Albom嘅書"},{"pid":"b0d5a01fee72c0171dfed0772e0a4b43542304a7","tid":741023,"uid":76632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:26:47.000Z","msg":"牧羊少年奇幻之旅"},{"pid":"4a5fa58a971de698e01e504294b23665db95e1de","tid":741023,"uid":176318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"憂鬱的熱帶"},{"pid":"b84a6450379b0b1709164dce817813b9734af71e","tid":741023,"uid":176318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5169359445c41220cd3a1b3df5bd2f9805583aa3","tid":741023,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:26:03.000Z","msg":"以前細個嗰時睇小王子都只係覺得好無聊，完全睇唔明。但人大左再睇翻，真係會令到自己感觸落淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以想問吓各位巴絲有冇小王子呢type嘅書推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"小毛驢與我 ----希美內思(西班牙現代詩人，曾獲1956年諾貝爾文學獎)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010386094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010386094&d=oC%2F2cbnt5wiLF736FStNPKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=17a38342\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010386094</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普兒 (Platero) 軀體嬌小，全身毛茸滑溜，聰明可愛，體貼又有耐性，是許多孩童的玩伴，也是作者的知己。牠在作者細膩生動的描繪下，躍然紙上，觸動了各地讀者的心。<br />\n<br />\n　　作者希美內思，是著名的西班牙現代詩人，曾獲1956年諾貝爾文學獎。《小毛驢與我》一書，以散文詩的形式，呈現他騎驢漫遊西班牙鄉間的感觸及見聞。感情真摯，想像豐富，引人入勝，<span style=\"color: red;\">與《小王子》齊名，是老少宜的抒情小品集，世界各國都有譯本。此中文新譯筆觸優美，多見巧思，為難得一見的佳作。</span>"},{"pid":"0878cd0afe49af11072e33b0d441c137df842a38","tid":741023,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e610d982e9a23f7af8fb89e6b36837500728257","tid":741023,"uid":147459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"面書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}